search.management

Class RecordReplica

  • java.lang.Object
    • search.management.RecordReplica
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RecordReplica
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

    Represents a replica of a ESGF Record of a Output Climate Model.

    Each record replica can be the master or a replica of a data output and share metadata about the information that they contain (data node, index node and services).

    Author:
    Karem Terry
